page.title: 19HAVING FUN IN STRATHNAIRN
page.content: {ROCK CLIMBING I have never been rock climbing but I have always wanted to.I know a lot of people that have been rock climbing. there are a lot of big rocks around our area with steep cliffs. {SWING PARK There is only one swing park in our area and it is a pretty good swing park.It only has two swings a round about and a chute.The swing park is only for little ones and I like the round about best of all because once when my uncle and aunte my uncle pushed me really fast.He nearly made me sick.I don't like being sick a lot because I always have a sore throat. {FISHNG The River Nairn was famous for its salmon until poachers poisoned it several years ago.It will be some time before it will be completely clear.
